bot ShoppingBot
domain ecommerce
tone friendly

welcome "Welcome to our store. How can I help? What do you want to buy?"

intent find_products
keywords: search find product item clothing
response "What would you like to find? We have clothes, shoes, and more."

intent check_price
keywords: cost price how much expensive
response "Prices vary. Check product pages for details on our website."

fallback "For more help, visit our store website or contact support"
